snippet.title: Updated Trailer
snippet.description:
Tear through a dark, atmospheric environment at lightning speeds, and battle violent machines and terrifying monsters in this fast-paced, physics-based metroidvania.  

Uncover the eldritch mystery behind civilization’s fall, and rise up against the transhumanist dystopia that took its place.    

Made in Unreal Engine 5.


Music:  onumi & LEViT∆TE - BLOODSEANCE
https://onumi.fanlink.to/bloodseance
